getStreamedAmount.t.sol
├── when the stream is null
│  └── it should return zero
└── when the stream is not null
   ├── when the start time is greater than the current time
   │  └── it should return zero
   ├── when the start time is equal to the current time
   │  └── it should return zero
   └── when the start time is less than the current time
      ├── when there is one segment
      │  └── it should return the correct streamed amount
      └── when there are multiple segments
         ├── when the current milestone is the 1st in the array
         │  └── it should return the correct streamed amount
         └── when the current milestone is not the 1st in the array
            └── it should return the correct streamed amount
